* From January 25 to February 6, 2008 – the Teigai Snow Disaster occurred; since this period fell before the Lunisolar's New Year (正月) and Spring Festival (春節), it is considered part of a Teigai year.

== 丁亥の月 ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙}}), the month of {{ill|October|ja|10月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Teigai|ja|丁亥}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬}} until the day before {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪}}) as applicable.

