=== Events ===
* In {{ill|Jitō Tennō|ja|持統天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jitō Tennō|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jitō Tennō|qq=}}'s 1st year (687 AD) – from the Asukaike Kōbō Ruins, {{ill|Tomihon-sen|ja|富本銭|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomihon-sen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomihon-sen|qq=}} were detected and wooden tablets inscribed with "丁亥年" were unearthed from the same soil layer, leading to the estimation that the Tomihon-sen were cast during this period.
* In {{ill|Ōei|ja|応永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei|qq=}} 14 (January 1408 AD) – the {{ill|Ōei Earthquake|ja|応永地震|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Earthquake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Earthquake|qq=}} occurred; it may have been confused with the Hōei Earthquake, which falls within the same Sexagenary cycle.
* In {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=}} 4 (1707 AD) – the "Teigai no Hen" (Crisis of 亥) occurred, marked by the {{ill|Hōei Earthquake|ja|宝永地震|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei Earthquake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei Earthquake|qq=}}<ref>[https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1390572174727612416 都司嘉宣(1981)] 都司嘉宣編: 高知県地震津波史料, 防災科学技術研究資料 57, i-253, 1981-03-20, 独立行政法人防災科学技術研究所</ref> and the {{ill|Hōei Great Eruption|ja|宝永大噴火|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei Great Eruption|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei Great Eruption|qq=}}.
* From January 25 to February 6, 2008 – the Teigai Snow Disaster occurred; since this period fell before the Lunisolar's New Year (正月) and Spring Festival (春節), it is considered part of a Teigai year.

== 丁亥の月 ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|lt=Kanoe (庚)|2=ja|3=庚|4=zh|5=庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|October|ja|10月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Winter|ja|立冬|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Winter|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Winter|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavy Snow|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavy Snow|qq=}}) as applicable.

