=== 選日 ===
The day of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=}}.

