i linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (i.e. Water overcomes Fire).
==Pronunciation== PronounceYin Fire Pig
==Years of Yin Fire Pig== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 27 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Fire Pig (丁亥)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 27|27 AD]] * [[:en:AD 87|87 AD]] * [[:en:AD 147|147 AD]] * [[:en:207|207 AD]] * [[:en:267|267 AD]] * [[:en:327|327 AD]] * [[:en:387|387 AD]] * [[:en:447|447 AD]] * [[:en:507|507 AD]] * [[:en:567|567 AD]] * [[:en:627|627 AD]] * [[:en:687|687 AD]] * [[:en:AD 747|747 AD]] * [[:en:807|807 AD]] * [[:en:867|867 AD]] * [[:en:927|927 AD]] * [[:en:987|987 AD]] | * [[:en:1047|1047 AD]] * [[:en:1107|1107 AD]] * [[:en:1167|1167 AD]] * [[:en:1227|1227 AD]] * [[:en:1287|1287 AD]] * [[:en:1347|1347 AD]] * [[:en:1407|1407 AD]] * [[:en:1467|1467 AD]] * [[:en:1527|1527 AD]] * [[:en:1587|1587 AD]] * [[:en:1647|1647 AD]] * [[:en:1707|1707 AD]] * [[:en:1767|1767 AD]] * [[:en:1827|1827 AD]] * [[:en:1887|1887 AD]] * [[:en:1947|1947 AD]] | * [[:en:2007|2007 AD]] * {{ill|2067 AD|ja|2067年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2067|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2067 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2127 AD|ja|2127年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2127|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2127 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2187 AD|ja|2187年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2187|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2187 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2247 AD|ja|2247年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2247|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2247 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2307 AD|ja|2307年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2307|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2307 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2367 AD|ja|2367年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2367|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2367 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2427 AD|ja|2427年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2427|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2427 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2487 AD|ja|2487年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2487|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2487 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2547 AD|ja|2547年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2547|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2547 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2607 AD|ja|2607年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2607|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2607 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2667 AD|ja|2667年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2667|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2667 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2727 AD|ja|2727年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2727|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2727 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2787 AD|ja|2787年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2787|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2787 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2847 AD|ja|2847年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2847|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2847 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2907 AD|ja|2907年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2907|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2907 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2967 AD|ja|2967年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2967|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2967 AD|qq=}} |}
=== Events === * In [[:en:Empress Jitō|Jitō Tennō]]'s 1st year (687 AD) – from the Asukaike Kōbō Ruins, [[:en:Fuhonsen|Tomihon-sen]] were detected and wooden tablets inscribed with "丁亥年" were unearthed from the same soil layer, leading to the estimation that the Tomihon-sen were cast during this period. * In [[:en:Ōei|Ōei]] 14 (January 1408 AD) – the {{ill|Ōei Earthquake|ja|応永地震|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Earthquake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Earthquake|qq=}} occurred; it may have been confused with the Hōei Earthquake, which falls within the same Sexagenary cycle. * In [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 4 (1707 AD) – the "Teigai no Hen" (Crisis of 亥) occurred, marked by the [[:en:1707 Hōei earthquake|Hōei Earthquake]]<ref>[https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1390572174727612416 都司嘉宣(1981)] 都司嘉宣編: 高知県地震津波史料, 防災科学技術研究資料 57, i-253, 1981-03-20, 独立行政法人防災科学技術研究所</ref> and the [[:en:Hōei eruption|Hōei Great Eruption]]. * From January 25 to February 6, 2008 – the Teigai Snow Disaster occurred; since this period fell before the Lunisolar's New Year (正月) and Spring Festival (春節), it is considered part of a Teigai year.
==Months of Yin Fire Pig== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|lt=Kanoe (庚)|2=ja|3=庚|4=zh|5=庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:October|October]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Lidong|Beginning of Winter]] until the day before [[:en:Daxue (solar term)|Heavy Snow]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yin Fire Pig== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}} is as follows. === 選日 === The day of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=}}.
