i linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|13=User:Immanuelle/Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (i.e. Water overcomes Fire).
==Pronunciation== * Yin Fire Pig (丁亥) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): dīnghài ** Cantonese (Jyutping): ding1 hoi6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: ひのといのしし (hinoto-inoshishi) ***Onyomi: ていかのいのしし (teika-no-inoshishi) ***Onyomi: ていがい (teigai) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): jeonghae ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Đinh Hợi
==Years of Yin Fire Pig== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 27 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Teigai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|丁亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teigai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Pig|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Fire Pig (丁亥)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 27|27 AD]] * [[:en:AD 87|87 AD]] * [[:en:AD 147|147 AD]] * [[:en:207|207 AD]] * [[:en:267|267 AD]] * [[:en:327|327 AD]] * [[:en:387|387 AD]] * [[:en:447|447 AD]] * [[:en:507|507 AD]] * [[:en:567|567 AD]] * [[:en:627|627 AD]] * [[:en:687|687 AD]] * [[:en:AD 747|747 AD]] * [[:en:807|807 AD]] * [[:en:867|867 AD]] * [[:en:927|927 AD]] * [[:en:987|987 AD]] | * [[:en:1047|1047 AD]] * [[:en:1107|1107 AD]] * [[:en:1167|1167 AD]] * [[:en:1227|1227 AD]] * [[:en:1287|1287 AD]] * [[:en:1347|1347 AD]] * [[:en:1407|1407 AD]] * [[:en:1467|1467 AD]] * [[:en:1527|1527 AD]] * [[:en:1587|1587 AD]] * [[:en:1647|1647 AD]] * [[:en:1707|1707 AD]] * [[:en:1767|1767 AD]] * [[:en:1827|1827 AD]] * [[:en:1887|1887 AD]] * [[:en:1947|1947 AD]] | * [[:en:2007|2007 AD]] * {{ill|2067 AD|ja|2067年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2067|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2067 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2127 AD|ja|2127年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2127|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2127 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2187 AD|ja|2187年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2187|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2187 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2247 AD|ja|2247年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2247|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2247 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2307 AD|ja|2307年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2307|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2307 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2367 AD|ja|2367年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|1